# HR Analytics Dashboard

This Power BI dashboard analyzes employee attrition, workforce demographics, and HR performance metrics to help organizations understand employee turnover and workforce trends.

## Tools Used
- Power BI
- Data Visualization
- Business Intelligence

## Dashboard Overview

This dashboard provides insights into:

- Employee attrition rate
- Attrition by education
- Attrition by age group
- Attrition by job role
- Attrition by years at company

## Key Insights

- Overall employee attrition rate
- Attrition distribution across departments
- Age group analysis of employee turnover
- Education level impact on attrition
